<h1>About Us</h1>
<img src="~/images/v.jpg" width="1150" height="450"/> <br /><br />
<p>It’s a familiar sight isn’t it? Women haggling with sabzi waalas, vegetables burning up in the sun,
    flies buzzing around and rates keep going up and down like it’s the stock market.
    Well, that ghastly visage is a thing of the past now. Say hi to TheFoodStaple.
    The name says it all.
    We got all the green and juicy that you need.
    From exotic vegetables like Zucchini, Pak Choi, LoloRoso to imported fruits like Kiwi, Dragonfruit 
    and Rambutan as well as run of the mill veggies such as carrots, radishes, brinjals, potatoes etc . 
    And it’s our guarantee, no one else can beat our prices, because there are no middlemen here, 
    it’s straight from the distributor’s basket.
    Don’t worry about the freshness or quality either, we deliver only the freshest of vegetables and fruites.</p>

